# Configuration for Podman AI Stack
# This file is used as an EnvironmentFile in the Quadlet containers.
# You can set any environment variables here that you want to pass to the containers.

# --- Open WebUI Configuration ---
# See: https://docs.openwebui.com/reference/env-configuration

# Connection to Ollama (default: http://localhost:11434)
# OLLAMA_BASE_URL=http://localhost:11434

# --- Ollama Configuration ---
# See: https://github.com/ollama/ollama/blob/main/docs/faq.md#how-do-i-configure-ollama-using-environment-variables

# Host address Ollama binds to (default: 0.0.0.0)
# OLLAMA_HOST=0.0.0.0
